<span style="color:#008000;"><span style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span>The museum used to be a 19th Century hunting lodge within the walls of the castle. Exhibits and exhibitions include lots of items of historical interest from the surrounding area.</span></span></span></p>
